4ng-xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-2wmddZOuhfvKpCrjp9Ks5g">Liêu Đông xuân nhật kỳ 1 - 遼東春日其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Trinh/author-HrCILDC9soRz0JVGAcDF9w">Lê Trinh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/Ng%E1%BA%ABu-nhi%C3%AAn-t%C3%A1c-k%E1%BB%B3-6/poem-pyYBU4FIo5dUSEVYV9KmZA">Ngẫu nhiên tác kỳ 6 - 偶然作其六</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/author-9f1Hth0gmM_PXzGNXg5Fog">Vương Duy</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/Qu%E1%BB%B7-ho%E1%BA%A1ch-t%E1%BB%AB-Gi%E1%BA%A3-B%E1%BA%A3o-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc/poem-zf9KF6NYoiyU_xgbBBCTSQ">Quỷ hoạch từ - Giả Bảo Ngọc - 姽嫿詞－賈寶玉</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/Ti%E1%BB%85n-ch%C3%ADnh-s%E1%BB%A9-L%C3%AA-Tu%E1%BA%A5n-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-nh%C3%A2n/poem-F2-3A9ZxGU9G096d4i8d9w">Tiễn chính sứ Lê Tuấn đại nhân - 餞正使黎峻大人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/author-h3EvqeQvlQUxq2sceUWWYQ">Đoàn Huyên</a>)<br></div>	</div>
